---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/accounting-precision/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="Services Overview | TaxPro & Partners"
  description="High-clarity financial solutions designed for modern corporate growth, from complex tax compliance to strategic business advisory."
  active="services"
  canonicalPath="/templates/accounting-precision/services"
>
<main class="pt-tp-xl pb-tp-xl px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-tp-container-max mx-auto">
<header class="mb-tp-xl text-center md:text-left max-w-3xl reveal-on-scroll">
<h1 class="font-tp-headline-xl text-tp-headline-lg-mobile md:text-tp-headline-xl text-primary mb-tp-md">Our Specialized Expertise</h1>
<p class="font-tp-body-lg text-tp-body-lg text-on-surface-variant">We provide high-clarity financial solutions designed for modern corporate growth. From complex tax compliance to strategic business advisory, we are your trusted partner in precision.</p>
</header>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-6 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter">
<div class="md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl corporate-shadow p-tp-lg flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[320px] reveal-on-scroll">
<div>
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-tp-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">account_balance_wallet</span>
</div>
<h2 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md text-primary mb-2">Tax Planning &amp; Compliance</h2>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl">Strategic tax structuring and meticulous filing for corporations and high-net-worth individuals. We ensure full compliance while optimizing your global tax footprint with precision and foresight.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-tp-lg">
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-secondary font-bold hover:underline" href="/templates/accounting-precision/services/tax-planning">
                        Learn More <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl corporate-shadow p-tp-lg flex flex-col justify-between reveal-on-scroll">
<div>
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-tp-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">verified_user</span>
</div>
<h2 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md text-primary mb-2">Audit &amp; Assurance</h2>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Rigorous financial examinations providing the highest level of assurance to stakeholders and regulators.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-tp-lg">
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-secondary font-bold hover:underline" href="/templates/accounting-precision/contact">
                        Learn More <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl corporate-shadow p-tp-lg flex flex-col justify-between reveal-on-scroll">
<div>
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-tp-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">insights</span>
</div>
<h2 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md text-primary mb-2">Business Advisory</h2>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Scalable corporate strategies, M&amp;A support, and risk management frameworks to drive enterprise value.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-tp-lg">
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-secondary font-bold hover:underline" href="/templates/accounting-precision/contact">
                        Learn More <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl corporate-shadow p-tp-lg flex flex-col justify-between reveal-on-scroll">
<div>
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-tp-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">receipt_long</span>
</div>
<h2 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md text-primary mb-2">Bookkeeping</h2>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Automated and highly organized financial records maintained with absolute professional integrity and clarity.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-tp-lg">
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-secondary font-bold hover:underline" href="/templates/accounting-precision/contact">
                        Learn More <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl corporate-shadow p-tp-lg flex flex-col justify-between reveal-on-scroll">
<div>
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-tp-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">monetization_on</span>
</div>
<h2 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md text-primary mb-2">Wealth Management</h2>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Personalized capital preservation and growth strategies for a secure and legacy-focused financial future.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-tp-lg">
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-secondary font-bold hover:underline" href="/templates/accounting-precision/contact">
                        Learn More <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Featured Image Interstitial -->
<section class="my-tp-xl rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative h-[400px] reveal-on-scroll">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/60 flex items-center px-tp-lg">
<div class="max-w-xl">
<h3 class="text-white font-tp-headline-lg text-tp-headline-lg mb-tp-md">Dedicated to Excellence in Corporate Finance</h3>
<p class="text-white/90 font-tp-body-lg text-tp-body-lg">Our partners bring decades of combined experience across diverse industries, from tech startups to global manufacturing conglomerates.</p>
</div>
</div>
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="A sophisticated corporate boardroom with a long table and floor-to-ceiling windows overlooking a city skyline." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD84G46POYX_yCIkd1HJGCMpsgiykdi0ypgxAB6OF28aeTKi-lGSm2srJWY8_aSP0Sg3HwhVO4M1NwmH3sPj00-lbG66Sxmk4BLhbhXGaeCW8g__OvQdm31f9svgVc_Xe6-yEXg9OgtbXugeDOcsV1mGIhaZy9xo952kDK84y9TQ2zBsNH8tYksjU1PCx9i6L3GQ0yzBepxxb_FJIaMbPto_Ap3sFD6eyHFHjB4-QctdaJyGk_z8cbuC0hDCwEmULwo2bxowG3zTgo" />
</section>
<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="bg-primary-container rounded-xl p-tp-xl text-center md:text-left flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-tp-lg reveal-on-scroll">
<div>
<h2 class="font-tp-headline-lg text-tp-headline-lg text-on-primary mb-2">Not sure which service you need?</h2>
<p class="font-tp-body-lg text-tp-body-lg text-on-primary-container">Speak with our advisors for a customized assessment of your financial landscape.</p>
</div>
<a class="whitespace-nowrap px-tp-xl py-tp-md bg-secondary text-on-primary rounded-lg font-tp-label-md text-tp-label-md hover:scale-105 transition-transform inline-block" href="/templates/accounting-precision/contact">
                Contact us today
            </a>
</section>
</main>
</TemplateLayout>
